  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomized controlled trial to evaluate the efficacy of oral iron supplementation plus&#xD;
      cofactors in reducing the prevalence of preoperative anemia in a cohort of 60 patients&#xD;
      undergoing elective prosthetic hip or knee surgery.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
